com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.text_to_speech.v1.model

Interface GetPronunciationOptions.Voice

  • Enclosing class:
    GetPronunciationOptions

    public static interface GetPronunciationOptions.Voice
    A voice that specifies the language in which the pronunciation is to be returned. All voices for the same language (for example, `en-US`) return the same translation.
